{"tid":1172741,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"行軍器廠街天橋去紅隧一問","createTime":"2019-05-26T15:44:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T14:58:46.000Z","uid":158074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6586395d37a7c0a663f643e803c740ff2f3b42b9","tid":1172741,"uid":158074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T15:44:18.000Z","msg":"演藝對出個條天橋，如果要去紅隧，基本上一落天橋就要立即cut 左，如果唔係好快之後就一路實線cut唔到去左線，但左線既車又行得好快下。大家係咪係落橋位收到好慢搵位cut 左呢？ 少過香港島，真心請教。<br />\n<br />\n反而，左線車要cut 右去東隧方向就大把位慢慢入。唔知點解cut 左去紅隧得咁短可以cut."},{"pid":"0f1196128beace9008c9ac0f9974d333280b480d","tid":1172741,"uid":99473,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T16:08:55.000Z","msg":"打死火燈<br />\n狂咁按呠呠<br />\n開埋高燈<br />\n死cut埋去<br />\n包架架車都讓你"},{"pid":"45791b00d65e8ca5180b3a3e44854f7e48cece88","tid":1172741,"uid":66242,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T12:47:17.000Z","msg":"唔知<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ae36e16bf804dd041bd89ed524c013ccb056e5","tid":1172741,"uid":91638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T14:33:28.000Z","msg":"入唔到咪停低架車等機會入<br />\n好多車係告士打道都係咁<br />\n唔剩止係入紅隧個啲<br />\n有啲要入最右線上鵝頸橋既車都係咁<br />\n<br />\n同埋繁忙時間軍器廠落橋位好似有慈母會分流兩邊既車入線<br />\n所以繁忙時間就更加唔使驚"},{"pid":"992f7756a2d918b483b6c3bc80621d08796bf35a","tid":1172741,"uid":67212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45791b00d65e8ca5180b3a3e44854f7e48cece88","tid":1172741,"uid":66242,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T12:47:17.000Z","msg":"唔知<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T14:54:29.000Z","msg":"西行兜灣北仲快過慢塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31ebcdc111a21eb47c66983942d2882866425c0","tid":1172741,"uid":29497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T14:55:02.000Z","msg":"呢段路好多時大家交叉行,不過會有d L樣搞串party